Taxa_Description: Calanus spp., Calanus minor, Eucalanus spp., Metridia lucens
Small Calanoid Copepods less than 1.6 mm Prosome length
Clupeidae- Atlantic herring, Atlantic menaden, Alosa spp.
Phycidae- Urophycis spp., Red hake, White hake, Spotted hake
Merlucciidae- Merluccius spp., Silver hake, Offshore hake
Pleuronectiformes- Citharichthys, Etropus, Syacium, Bothus, Hippoglossina, Trichopsetta
Pleuronectiformes- Paralichthys, Pseudopleuronectes, Hippoglossoides, Hippoglossus, Limanda, Glyptocephalus
